<h2 id="purpose">Purpose</h2>

<p>Online News outlets already have ‚Äúsearch box‚Äù. When you write some keyword to here you get results. However problem starts in the detail.  Intentionally or just a result of poor algorithm the results includes a  lot of irrelevant result.  I experienced it while I scraped the local news from Turkish news sites. To overcome this problem I decided to build my own artificial intelligence tool to detect really local news and non-local news that listed in the search results of the local news keyword.</p>

<p>I  build a machine learning algorithm for classifying Turkish News in terms of ‚Äòlocal news‚Äô or ‚Äònon-local news‚Äô. The main motivation behind this algorithm is the fuzzy nature of search pages of news outlets. Most of the web pages inject non-local headlines into local news. This algorithm will detect the real nature of the headline.</p>

<p>For this purpose, I scraped the local and non-local news based on special queries. Then I trained multiple algorithms to find the best fit. Linear SVC model winned. <a href="/2020/01/26/yerel_mi_degilmi_siniflandirici/" target="_blank">Here is my algorithm</a>. With Python language.</p>

<p>The accuracy of prediction power of the algorithm according to the cross validation of overall data is more than %95.</p>

